010#These three defines exist in OpenGL.GL, but does not correspond to those used here
011GL_GEOMETRY_SHADER_EXT       = 0x8DD9
012GL_GEOMETRY_INPUT_TYPE_EXT   = 0x8DDB
013GL_GEOMETRY_OUTPUT_TYPE_EXT  = 0x8DDC
014GL_GEOMETRY_VERTICES_OUT_EXT = 0x8DDA

016# 1:
017# Define the missing glProgramParameteri method
018_glProgramParameteri = None
019def glProgramParameteri( program, pname, value  ):
020    global _glProgramParameteri
021    if not _glProgramParameteri:
022        import ctypes
023        # Open the opengl32.dll
024        gldll = ctypes.windll.opengl32
025        # define a function pointer prototype of *(GLuint program, GLenum pname, GLint value)
026        prototype = ctypes.WINFUNCTYPE( ctypes.c_int, ctypes.c_uint, ctypes.c_uint, ctypes.c_int )
027        # Get the win gl func adress
028        fptr = gldll.wglGetProcAddress( 'glProgramParameteriEXT' )
029        if fptr==0:
030            raise Exception( "wglGetProcAddress('glProgramParameteriEXT') returned a zero adress, which will result in a nullpointer error if used.")
031        _glProgramParameteri = prototype( fptr )
032    _glProgramParameteri( program, pname, value )
033 
034# 2:
035# Define the missing glCreateShaderObject method
036_glCreateShaderObject = None
037def glCreateShaderObject( shadertype ):
038    global _glCreateShaderObject
039    if not _glCreateShaderObject:
040        import ctypes
041        # Open the opengl32.dll
042        gldll = ctypes.windll.opengl32
043        # define a function pointer prototype of *(GLuint program, GLenum pname, GLint value)
044        prototype = ctypes.WINFUNCTYPE( ctypes.c_int, ctypes.c_uint )
045        # Get the win gl func adress
046        fptr = gldll.wglGetProcAddress( 'glCreateShaderObjectARB' )
047        if fptr==0:
048            raise Exception( "wglGetProcAddress('glCreateShaderObjectARB') returned a zero adress, which will result in a nullpointer error if used.")
049        _glCreateShaderObject = prototype( fptr )
050    return _glCreateShaderObject( shadertype )

052vert = '''
053void main(){
054    gl_FrontColor = gl_Color;
055    gl_Position = ftransform();
056}
057'''
058 
059geom = '''#version 120
060#extension GL_EXT_geometry_shader4 : enable
061const float radius = 0.5;
062varying out vec2 coord;
063 
064void main()
065{
066  gl_FrontColor = gl_FrontColorIn[0];
067 
068  coord = vec2( -1,-1 );
069  gl_Position = (gl_PositionIn[0] + gl_ProjectionMatrix * vec4(-radius,-radius,0,0) );
070  EmitVertex();
071  coord = vec2( -1,1 );
072  gl_Position = (gl_PositionIn[0] + gl_ProjectionMatrix * vec4(-radius,radius, 0,0) );
073  EmitVertex();
074  coord = vec2( 1,-1 );
075  gl_Position = (gl_PositionIn[0] + gl_ProjectionMatrix * vec4( radius,-radius, 0,0) );
076  EmitVertex();
077  coord = vec2( 1,1 );
078  gl_Position = (gl_PositionIn[0] + gl_ProjectionMatrix * vec4( radius,radius, 0,0) );
079  EmitVertex(); 
080  EndPrimitive();
081}
082'''
083frag = '''
084varying in vec2 coord;
085void main(){
086    vec4 color = gl_Color;
087    color.a = 1.0-length( coord );
088    if (color.a<0.0) discard;
089 
090    // A VERY FAKE "lighting" model
091    float d = dot( normalize(vec3(coord,1.0)), vec3( 0.19, 0.19, 0.96225 ) );
092    color.rgb *= d*d;
093    // end "lighting"
094     
095    gl_FragColor = color;
096}
097'''

099theta = 0.0
100delta = 0.0
101TIMEOUTFACTOR = 5.0
102 
103def my_idle( ):
104    global theta
105    global delta
106    t = time.clock()
107    passed = t-delta
108    theta += passed
109    delta = t
110 
111    dirvector = numpy.array( [ -1-(math.sin( theta/2.0 )), -1-(math.cos(theta/2.0)), 1.0 ] )
112    dirvector *=  (1.0 / math.sqrt( (dirvector**2).sum() ) )
113     
114 
115    global POINTS
116    global VEL
117    global TIMES
118 
119    #Add "gravity" to all the velocities
120    VEL[:,2] -= passed * 9.81 * 5
121    #Increment positions according to velocities
122    POINTS += passed*VEL
123     
124    pbelow_zero = POINTS[:,2] < 0.0
125    # "drag" all points below zero (in z) up again
126    POINTS[pbelow_zero] *= [1,1,0]
127    # Change the z velocity for all "collisions" with the zero z plane
128    VEL[ pbelow_zero ] *= [1,1,-1.0]
129 
130    # add passed seconds to all points timeout
131    TIMES += passed
132 
133    timeouts = TIMES > TIMEOUTFACTOR
134    TIMES[timeouts] = numpy.random.random( timeouts.sum() ) * 0.1 * TIMEOUTFACTOR
135    VEL[timeouts] = dirvector + 0.5*numpy.random.random( timeouts.sum() * 3 ).reshape( (-1,3) )
136    VEL[timeouts] *= 50.0
137    POINTS[timeouts] = [0.0,0.0,0.0]
138     
139    glutPostRedisplay()
140 
141shader_program = None
142def define_shader():
143    global shader_program
144    shader_program = gl.glCreateProgram()  
145    glProgramParameteri(shader_program, GL_GEOMETRY_INPUT_TYPE_EXT, gl.GL_POINTS )
146    glProgramParameteri(shader_program, GL_GEOMETRY_OUTPUT_TYPE_EXT, gl.GL_TRIANGLE_STRIP )
147    glProgramParameteri(shader_program, GL_GEOMETRY_VERTICES_OUT_EXT, 4 )
148 
149    vobj = glCreateShaderObject( GL_VERTEX_SHADER )
150    glShaderSource( vobj, vert )
151    glCompileShader( vobj )
152    print glGetShaderInfoLog(vobj)
153    glAttachShader( shader_program, vobj )
154     
155    gobj = glCreateShaderObject( GL_GEOMETRY_SHADER_EXT )
156    glShaderSource( gobj, geom)   
157    glCompileShader( gobj )
158    print glGetShaderInfoLog(gobj)
159    glAttachShader( shader_program, gobj )
160 
161    fobj = glCreateShaderObject( GL_FRAGMENT_SHADER )
162    glShaderSource( fobj, frag)   
163    glCompileShader( fobj )
164    print glGetShaderInfoLog(fobj)
165    glAttachShader( shader_program, fobj )
166     
167    glLinkProgram( shader_program )
168    print glGetProgramInfoLog(shader_program)

171def reshape( width, height ):
172   glViewport(0, 0, width, height);
173   glMatrixMode(GL_PROJECTION);
174   glLoadIdentity();
175   gluPerspective(65.0, width / float(height), 1, 1000 );
176   glMatrixMode(GL_MODELVIEW);
177 
178POINTS = None
179COLORS = None
180VEL = None
181TIMES = None
182def display( ):  
183   glClear(GL_COLOR_BUFFER_BIT | GL_DEPTH_BUFFER_BIT ) 
184   glLoadIdentity()  
185   gluLookAt( 60.0,60.0,25.0,
186              0.0,0.0,0.0,
187              0.0,0.0,1.0 )
188   
189 
190   #glRotate( theta*10.0, 0.0,0.0,1.0 )
191   glTranslatef( 25.0,25.0,0 )
192    
193   #glEnable( GL_BLEND )
194   glBlendFunc( GL_SRC_ALPHA, GL_ONE )
195   glUseProgram( shader_program )
196   glEnableClientState( GL_COLOR_ARRAY )
197   glEnableClientState( GL_VERTEX_ARRAY )
198   glColorPointer( 3,GL_FLOAT,0,COLORS )
199   glVertexPointer(3,GL_FLOAT,0,POINTS )
200   glDrawArrays( 0,0, len( POINTS ) )
